## 34. A Transcription Playback Loop

Transcribe audio, then speak the transcription back:

```scheme
;; Listen, transcribe, and echo
(define captured (record 3.0))
(define text (speech/listen captured))
(speech/say text)
```

*[needs: record, speech/listen, speech/say]*  
<!-- BUILD: record, STT, TTS -->

The system listens, interprets, and repeats—an echo with a round trip through text.

