## 37. A Sung Transcription

Transcribe a sung melody (pitch detection + note sequence) instead of words:

```scheme
;; Transcribe a sung melody to note names
(define captured (record 4.0))
(transcribe captured)
```

*[needs: record, transcribe verb for audio → note sequence]*  
<!-- BUILD: record, pitch detection + note segmentation -->

This is a bridge to Chapter 14 (Transcription & Transposition). The `transcribe` verb returns a list of note events; `speech/listen` returns words. Both are inverses of synthesis.

